.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, strawberry, peach, carrot
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, board-games, filmmaking, cooking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, rugby, water-polo
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's sport is rugby##2
6. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating kiwi and the person eating peach##2
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | peach | strawberry  | kiwi | carrot      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | cooking  | hiking | board-games |
| Sport   | water-polo | basketball | biathlon | rugby     |

