.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, grapefruit, tomato, mango
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, family, scientific, disaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, skiing, sailing, golf
1. the person who's sport is golf is the person watching family movies##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is between the person watching family movies and the person watching scientific movies##2
7. the person eating mango is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | tomato  | grapefruit    | mango | radish  |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | disaster       | family        | fantasy    |
| Sport         | skiing | soccer | golf  | sailing |

