.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, card-games, traveling, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, documentary, scientific, sports
4 different pets are kept: rat, dog, chinchilla, snake
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the owner of the snake and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | puzzles  | card-games | traveling | dancing |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | sports | documentary   | scientific         |
| Pet           | rat | chinchilla  | dog   | snake      |

