1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person eating pineapple##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the fan of hip-hop and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | grapefruit  | pineapple    | watermelon | pumpkin       |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking | drawing  | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | electronic      | gospel  | punk     |

