The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, horror, action
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
2. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
3. the person eating corn is between the person eating apricot and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
7. the person watching action movies is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person watching epic movies is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
