.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, nectarine, pineapple, cucumber
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, collecting, hiking, fishing
4 different pets are kept: fish, turtle, hedgehog, goldfish
1. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person eating nectarine##1
3. the owner of the fish is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the owner of the fish and the person eating cucumber##2
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the turtle##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | cucumber  | pineapple | pepper | nectarine     |
| Hobby   | woodworking | hiking   | fishing  | collecting    |
| Pet     | turtle        | goldfish       | fish      | hedgehog |

