The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, woodworking, camping, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: hamster, mouse, snake, dog
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking tea and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | water | tea     | hot-chocolate | soy-milk       |
| Hobby      | camping  | magic-tricks | rock-climbing  | woodworking |
| Pet        | dog  | mouse      | snake        | hamster      |

