3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | 7up | cola  | iced-tea       | juice   |
| Hobby      | board-games     | puzzles | woodworking | writing |
| Pet        | chinchilla        | hedgehog | goldfish     | bird |

