4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the scooter is between the person watching epic movies and the dressmaker##2
6. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the scooter is the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
