.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, cooking, card-games, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, engineer, photographer, dancer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, tennis, rowing, lacrosse
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the dancer##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is between the architect and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
6. the photographer is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | card-games   | cooking           | video-games         | puzzles      |
| Job     | architect | photographer | dancer | engineer |
| Sport   | rowing     | tennis         | soccer       | lacrosse        |

