3. the person drinking water is the fan of punk##1
4. the person drinking water is between the fan of ambient and the colombian##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
6. the australian is between the egyptian and the fan of pop##2
7. the fan of salsa is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
