.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, water, sprite
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, spinach, blueberry, pear
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton, cycling, skateboarding
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
2. the person eating blueberry is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
7. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | fanta | sprite           | water |
| Food       | eggplant | blueberry    | spinach          | pear   |
| Sport      | cycling  | badminton   | skateboarding | lacrosse  |

