.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, cola, sprite, almond-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, crime, spy
4 different pets are kept: turtle, bird, snake, hamster
1. the person watching crime movies is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking water is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the owner of the hamster is between the person drinking cola and the owner of the turtle##2
7. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | water | cola     | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | spy        | crime  | drama  |
| Pet           | turtle      | hamster         | bird | snake |

