1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the paramedic##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person driving the trike##1
3. the firefighter is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is the lawyer##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | firefighter        | lawyer  | paramedic | teacher   |
| Sport       | skiing | tennis | lacrosse    | swimming |
| Transport   | trike        | snowmobile     | jet-ski       | van      |

