.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, apricot, banana, spinach
4 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, turtle, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, boat, car, scooter
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
2. the person eating peas is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
4. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the scooter is the owner of the lizard##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the person eating spinach and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | spinach | apricot | peas | banana |
| Pet         | frog       | mouse     | turtle   | lizard   |
| Transport   | taxi | boat | car | scooter |

 